{
  "_id": "a6a2d243-1cb5-4271-898c-658064bc540e",
  "body": [
    {
      "_key": "79da68a478be4eaaacbbe076cadd4e2b",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "a085f4f4f2f04709bc201034f210b011",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "イントロダクション"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "57374efbc164451b8daf4518cd1c55a5",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "5a8d61e870834b80949f7f91be83022f",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "看護助手として「もう限界かも」と感じるのは珍しくありません。人手不足、夜勤続き、理不尽なやり取り。わたし自身も現場で同じ壁にぶつかり、体も心もすり減った経験があります。このしんどさは、あなた一人のせいではなく、現場の構造的な負荷が重なっているからです。まずは自分を責めず、「どう動けば安全で後悔の少ない道を選べるか」を一緒に整理しましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "79c9293317d54a0990e4fc9360857fa2",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "88ea7a546303440281fbf6b198a8b89e",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "看護助手が辞めたいと感じるリアルな理由"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "3e3f7271c6644eb0b0d7bc015ba0b2f5",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "2060359e72a947c6966c61c0209c93a1",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "給料が上がりにくく、責任や業務量に見合わないと感じること。人手不足で休憩も削られ、感謝より「もっとやって」が多い現場。コミュニケーションのすれ違いで心が削られ、腰や膝の痛みが蓄積し、夜勤で生活リズムが壊れていく。どれもよくある悩みで、あなたが弱いわけではありません。まずは「つらい」と口に出していいと受け止めてください。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "reference-4e57dbd4-92b8-41de-9f2a-e4ce788de32a",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-label-7f3fb779-ab17-4335-af0e-2d9bdd13b335",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "参考: "
        },
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-link-1770ee16-33e0-49a7-a848-13e00dcad069",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "link-bcc373cf-dbbc-4415-b5af-21e7e95773f7"
          ],
          "text": "厚生労働省 職業情報提供サイト（看護助手）"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-bcc373cf-dbbc-4415-b5af-21e7e95773f7",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://shigoto.mhlw.go.jp/User/Occupation/Detail/246?utm_source=chatgpt.com"
        }
      ],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "4197dbe556a2498fa0e8425b49a3a28d",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "29e25f4c986740d0b3e97eec60aa2f58",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "退職を考えたらまずやるべき準備"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "3109f40d0ec84a298836f4880a1faff2",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "5b709a914a5d43ecba52a53356c07948",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "退職理由の整理：本音（負担、賃金、人間関係）と、伝える建前（家庭都合、キャリア見直し）を切り分けておくと話しやすくなります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "f6cdee290ddc4acd9ddcc870ca1a02e3",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "5e5343936059471c8c003a37580d7e40",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "有給残日数の確認と消化計画：退職日から逆算して、早めに申請するスケジュールをメモに。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "33c225e3a2c0425dbd7b37bf08c1e267",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "60e97adce4514f46a65c6f2d67f6dc92",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "給与締め日、保険、離職票の確認：月末締めか、社保切替・雇用保険手続きのスケジュールを把握しておくと安心です。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "5f5f8fea28ec485589f1e2a96f174f27",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "eec177e035374c8a9a0cf672ba24a7f6",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "トラブル防止メモ：上司とのやり取り、引き継ぎ内容、シフト調整を簡単に記録しておくと交渉の根拠になります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "0b6aac114b50447f8135348c74a3e6dc",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "8732a9b398e04652b9c54b7912ce98bf",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "信頼できる人に相談：同僚、家族、労組、専門窓口。感情の整理と第三者の視点があるだけで、決断の重さが少し軽くなります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "reference-1748cfd4-2ce0-4b27-8a2c-7216a04c53fb",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-label-e576ba17-b345-4a9a-aac8-f7cc11b8bb83",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "参考: "
        },
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-link-17d4437f-6118-4a23-a5f1-eecce0beac83",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "link-d5ed64eb-8aea-4c06-9aa6-bbf5ed1c5356"
          ],
          "text": "NsPace Career 看護助手の転職・年収コラム"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-d5ed64eb-8aea-4c06-9aa6-bbf5ed1c5356",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://ns-pace-career.com/media/tips/01230/?utm_source=chatgpt.com"
        }
      ],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "08fa47c7f8a846eb978e13b7d40a5d33",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "da75f6ac285d4464afcdc8903b099070",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "看護助手が取れる3つの退職方法"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "d690e0f8b33a4e78a93094a430c187df",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "e676b6ace8dc477786e29f16047d9fbd",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "自分で退職を伝える"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "a257f91c97de45aeb684fd70b921cbb9",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "4a4e181ba22c40a588c980a11a23c371",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "費用ゼロで進められます。職場との関係が極端に悪くなく、交渉に慣れている人向け。引き継ぎを自分で段取りできる余力があるなら、もっともシンプルです。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "394333eb276b4275a70d3910ba9e48b1",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "09ceff17df0946849f985e0c05f62647",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "退職代行サービスを利用する"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "7fc7dc7bf6c74ea684b91179588d95cc",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "ac41adb097704b3db1402bb866531ffa",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "連絡や交渉を任せられます。上司と話すのが怖い、ハラスメントがある、即日で職場を離れたい場合に有効です。弁護士・労組運営を選べば法的にも安心度が高くなります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "21a1c061e637440a9510557314e5c286",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "0c85922fe69748139fe5e29a352508fc",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "サポートを受けながら自分で伝える（セルフ退職）"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "4aa6e01cae7c4c099285ad04b4ae2ca8",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "f494b10d0ffb4c13a47eed90f6e1b401",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "テンプレや相談を受けつつ、自分名義で進める方法。コストを抑えたいが手順に不安がある人向けです。メッセージ文例が欲しいときにも有効です。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "87b199b39df7400dac8499d84e6b6f14",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "4c7fb0813a11484d8eb4bad49b228e94",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "比較の目安"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "9adc9dc1e889422cb32f376e7b8fc759",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "1c264cad84174062aae9358b5f02e4ec",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "・自分で伝える: 0円 / 即日性△ / 法的安心度△"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "f0ecbc330395428985cefa2018dd2f5d",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "c719d0e3863d474dacc9688e611370d8",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "・退職代行: 数万円 / 即日性◎ / 法的安心度○〜◎（弁護士・労組なら◎）"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "3799c80a10624e62808c80c654b77624",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "8c66ab1dfe2c43c99368066b25042e6f",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "・セルフ退職: 低〜中コスト / 即日性○（テンプレ依存） / 安心度△〜○"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "b607907a4cf9482c92894b947b1cafa6",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "1d27a9012b924bfcb4ed60c6891385c3",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "それぞれの方法で「いまの自分にとって何が一番ラクか」を基準に選んで大丈夫です。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "588bea23c3fa433695f1603bb3613a25",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "cd5a9d8a4ca346b291339a0770972ace",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "退職代行を使う場合・使わない場合の差分"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "92e6658da86e444881ca36b6dbf0d93b",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "696a2f1b01cb420dbd1f602c30e27d92",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "使わない場合：上司との面談や引き継ぎの段取りを自分で行う必要があります。日程調整のストレスはあるものの、費用を抑えられ、関係が悪くない職場なら円満退職しやすいメリットもあります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "4654d9d920d441fc87b6a66e37a3685a",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "65177f533fe743349895f12a77cc3c76",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "使う場合：連絡や交渉を任せられるので、心理的・時間的な負担が大きく減ります。特にハラスメントや強い引き止めがある場合、第三者が間に入ることで安全に進められます。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "fbe0879bae754d8c85fd134964848cff",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "2f3647c460dc4bb388d43fa40e20cd2c",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "選び方のポイント：弁護士・労組など合法運営か、医療介護の相談実績があるか、24時間相談できるか、即日対応の可否。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "eb86eb04f8b047ed99e39ed4043656ad",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "ca1387e6466d44119831f879a15d61bd",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "さらに詳しい比較は退職代行3社の徹底比較記事も参考にしてください。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "59de3a9024544d24aa1f64afc894d7f6",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "3051668a7615462c8b7782787ae34392",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "自分で退職を伝える場合のポイント"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "b55b5e24f767487d9c7478b8c3bcf0b6",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "a1b64bfd078e4aa184b79f740dcec69e",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "・伝え方テンプレ：「家庭の事情で○月末に退職を希望します。引き継ぎは文書で準備しますので、日程をご相談させてください。」"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "2ddcf9cd7f3b45bf9274be493cab3a23",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "0f0c8381b969436daa8ec9f66d89ba3b",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "・本音を建前に変える：人手不足→家庭都合・キャリア見直し、賃金不満→別分野で経験を積みたい。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "9bdd26de105b4979b820461088a5aef3",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "fd67ecccac3c4bba836cb7de30c060e6",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "・引き止め回避：退職日は確定ベースで伝え、延長は難しいと先に言う。引き継ぎ内容と期限をセットで提示し、感情論ではなくスケジュールで会話する。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "4e565947e1a448ac8ab2d3c7150c4efd",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "06573ade16ca41afb3a17b8f0870ae2f",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "・スケジュール：意思表明→退職日確定→引き継ぎ→有給消化→離職票・証明書の受領。無理せず少しずつ進める。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "5f7f62f92f154d2e818eb920ad41e88f",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "93e7e81196f641e1841d0ab83d700812",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "退職代行サービスの安全性と選び方"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "84e9764886694dd8ae034fcfb4a7697f",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "870486bb83e546e5b82de7f8eacc246f",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "弁護士／労働組合を推奨：法的交渉や書類対応を適法に行えるため、未払賃金や有休消化の交渉も安心度が上がります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "ba8ea3a7c3004710acfebedf8d3d0c98",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "37d604186f904f6e85a1084e4efa53bf",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "非弁業者のリスク：不当請求、手続き不備、トラブル時に対応できない可能性があります。合法運営か、実績と口コミをできるだけ確認。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "cab1b89424844b4692ba8cf0fd9a1a6b",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "90c1fa222be54dbfbfd3ffae9cec7415",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "医療現場で起こりがちなトラブル：有休消化の交渉がうまくいかない、退職書類が遅れる、引き継ぎ拒否を理由に退職を渋られる、など。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "3c8b62faead64275803605f61c953d7f",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "4cebe2e5476e42f89a5acd8d804869b0",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "進行イメージ：無料相談→申込・支払い→会社連絡（代行）→退職意思伝達→書類・精算確認→完了。流れを知るだけでも不安は軽くなります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "5656e6f6c29043beb08d4f52a1f22eb3",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "8e9a32b67da24cf48b3127e2d010d669",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "安心して利用できる退職代行サービス比較（3社）"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "fd53e54685da453098ebcbe79f6d3c59",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "45bf92e5f86a4314a8d6fc11cebdca19",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "弁護士法人みやび（法的安心・全国対応）"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "ebc15b36306441a28a804e2e865de9cc",
